  "description": "A nighttime panoramic view of a city skyline with a prominent bridge spanning across dark water. Vivid fireworks are exploding in the sky above the city, adding a burst of color. The bridge is illuminated with white and red lights, stretching across the frame. The city itself is a tapestry of illuminated buildings, with varying heights and densities of lights. In the distance, the cityscape blends into a dark, hilly landscape. The overall effect is one of vibrant urban life against the backdrop of the night sky.",
